item.title: How do i make a new starting point?
item.dc:creator: @invalid_name1 invalid name
item.description:
@invalid_name1 wrote:

Open up player.java

Ctrl>f

paste this in

// the first call to updateThisPlayerMovement() will craft the proper initialization packet

you should see

teleportToX = 2794; teleportToY = 3181;

change the numbers at end to your start position.
